    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has plenty of life left in it for all your upcoming adventures! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
