      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that still catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is clean and supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and screen functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium audio system. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the utmost care. It delivers a smooth, responsive ride with crisp gear shifts and confident braking, thanks to a recent service that included a full fluid flush and brake pad replacement. It has been garage-kept and strictly maintained on a regular schedule, with no known mechanical issues or warning lights. While it bears the gentle marks of a car that has been enjoyed, it remains in impressive shape and is ready to provide many more miles of reliable, stylish transportation.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
